  StyleBox["c", "TI"]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "61a3d8bc-b443-4b2b-b19e-1fc284f237fc"],
 " is one of the most frequently used combination. Unfortunately, the \
Mathematica system reserves the symbol ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  TemplateBox[{
    Cell[
     TextData["N"]], "paclet:ref/N"},
   "RefLink",
   BaseStyle->{"InlineFormula"}]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "05fe2aea-b2d7-42bd-9d96-28cff155b2dc"],
 " for built-in operations. Therefore, we use ",
